{"id":"changes-of-raiment","term":"Changes of raiment","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Were reckoned among the treasures of rich men (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 45:22\">Gen. 45:22</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 14:12\">Judg. 14:12</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 14:13\">13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 5:22\">2 Kings 5:22</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 5:23\">23</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 45:22","Judges 14:12","Judges 14:13","2 Kings 5:22","2 Kings 5:23"]}